Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveMusic executive, Soso Soberekon, has lamented the increase in the rate of traffic robberies in different areas in Lagos State.
According to Soberekon, attacks taking place inside Lagos traffic were getting rampant and in need of urgent action from the Lagos State Governor, Babajide Sanwo-Olu.
